{"tid":385001,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會睇台灣直播 麥卡貝呀魯蛋lng咁呀","createTime":"2017-09-02T19:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T10:39:17.000Z","uid":29996,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416dad358ff7ee9c31b1b8c0123bbf53e56850b9","tid":385001,"uid":29996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"利申定先 我都係9成睇youtube精華 唔係咁好彩得閑睇聽直播<br />\n一開始係幾年前睇大中天精華<br />\n之後斷斷續續咁搵魯蛋精華睇<br />\n再睇下老皮<br />\n睇睇下又無睇老皮 但見到魯蛋同六嘆打機好好笑就睇埋六嘆<br />\n近排就直情返工都開住lng精華聽 發現六嘆鳥屎兩表兄弟真係幾撚搞笑就再dig d野黎睇 去麥卡貝睇埋現在宅知道<br />\n中間又有睇下女女咁 鍾共旗下員工葉子又睇下<br />\n<br />\n統神我無玩lol所以接觸唔多啦 但唔多講都好多人睇<br />\n行玩遊戲台個幾月都會講一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個post咁既鐘數開 都係睇完lng直播開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531a798d915793b2442580d4f5fcaf8f900e87ae","tid":385001,"uid":50384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:52:29.000Z","msg":"木曜四超玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da35cfcba5b1c1e9303b943fed49aac1f56e4109","tid":385001,"uid":96877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>木曜四超玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真係100分 <br />\n一日系列睇上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ebc7c76e03a432558190c6bd9e00facad6a114","tid":385001,"uid":50384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu